{"tid":1569294,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"內地網民「為阿sir送特產」 送炒米鹽水鴨被海關退回","createTime":"2019-09-14T14:32:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T14:40:48.000Z","uid":68738,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1afc6cbed3830a4ea9d4e25a5761117512907297","tid":1569294,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T14:32:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190914/large/1568443732_f514.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190914%2Flarge%2F1568443732_f514.jpg&h=13df5ce7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190914/large/1568443608_5fd9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190914%2Flarge%2F1568443608_5fd9.jpg&h=fca55374&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n內地網民發起「#我為阿sir送特產」號召。(互聯網)<br />\n<br />\n葵涌警署外一名「光頭士沙」劉澤基舉槍的畫面被媒體拍下，內地網民大讚：「非常感謝！也希望通過你們，告訴內地同胞知道，我們大部份香港人是正常的。加油！加油！」他們除了近日從深圳出發，響應微博「#我為阿sir送特產」的號召，將650盒月餅送到新界北總區警察總部、葵青警區總部暨青衣分區警署，以及元朗警署宿舍外；更有遠至內蒙的特產炒米、奶茶；南京的鹽水鴨；以及浙江的茶葉送到香港。<br />\n<br />\n由於中港口岸不允許大量食品帶入，網民以快遞寄送包裹又被海關退回。網民改變策略，選擇在香港大批購買月餅，然後「自行送貨」到警察手上。但是，因為中秋臨近，月餅供不應求，很多地方沒有庫存。來自深圳、福建、上海、浙江4地的網民說：「我們自己湊錢，包車去收月餅券！」<br />\n<br />\n根據《公務員實務守則》，香港公務員只可保留3種禮物，包括禮物的價值不超過500港元或公務員薪水的千分之一；二是禮物上刻有該公務員姓名的，1,500港元以上的禮物，公務員一般不敢保留自用，否則有可能觸犯法律；三是官員以嘉賓身份出席一些正式活動受贈價值不超過500港元的禮物。不過，即使公務員可保留上述價錢以下的物品，但一定也要填寫申報表。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190914/60044087?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190914%2F60044087%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=XCDgL7937Usx1GlZVM45wSZO8jd1M6XCUNMtuDfdPZA%3D&h=0b5e3419\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190914%2F60044087%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=ed1b798f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190914/60044087?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"7d0d2b9fd0eaccb86f86359f6be4e6764b0b5be7","tid":1569294,"uid":234159,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T14:33:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聽日見！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ktW8Y1Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FktW8Y1Q.jpg&h=d39b859f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1veB7Va.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1veB7Va.jpg&h=d08508ed&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e88280bec728b076afffd961a931de8fbce32034","tid":1569294,"uid":14449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T14:34:57.000Z","msg":"我係黑警都唔撚要支那野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"648999304355a2e780050878f8e0edca812780dd","tid":1569294,"uid":275370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T14:37:22.000Z","msg":"好柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9f9fac5abbe8f2ebf7d5da92d140b61986c7772","tid":1569294,"uid":126731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T14:40:22.000Z","msg":"比popo 嘆元素週期表<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e85727aef0816c8870b4f08ecb4840509254fbc","tid":1569294,"uid":264637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e88280bec728b076afffd961a931de8fbce32034","tid":1569294,"uid":